headline: Morgan Stanley Raises CSX Price Target Amid Positive Freight Outlook
summary: CSX Corporation (NASDAQ:CSX) is included among the 15 Best Stocks to Buy for the Long Term. On December 8, Morgan Stanley raised its price target on CSX Corporation (NASDAQ:CSX) to $30 from $27 while maintaining an Equal Weight rating on the shares. headline: CSX (CSX): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: CSX trades at $37.04 and has moved in lockstep with the market. Its shares have returned 14.6% over the last six months while the S&P 500 has gained 13.6%.
